(638,	149,	'_elementor_data',	'[{\"id\":\"c55b36c\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"stretch_section\":\"section-stretched\",\"layout\":\"full_width\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"765f181\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"44dc14a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"shortcode\":\"[hbupro_banner id=\\\"151\\\"]\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"shortcode\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"49ca628\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"44c241b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"628dd8d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"tabs\":[{\"tab_title\":\"Your partner in digital transformation\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>In today\\u2019s exponential explosion of technologies, it is imperative for every company to disrupt itself before the industry disrupts and eliminates it. Along with the shift of technologies is the shift of business models and organizational cultures that add to the pressures of not only coping with but leading the pack. The variety of solutions, methodologies and services also add to the confusion of business leaders.<\\/p><p>Amidst how complicated the business world has become,\\u00a0<span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">bneXt<\\/span>\\u00a0helps you find what you want to\\u00a0<span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">BE NEXT\\u00a0<\\/span>as a company and help you plot your course and create a roadmap towards\\u00a0<span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">Digital Transformation\\u00a0<\\/span>where each of the segments defined are in sync with your objectives, priorities, structure and culture.\\u00a0<\\/p><p>Beyond the roadmap,\\u00a0<span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">bneXt<\\/span>\\u00a0helps you execute each defined segment by providing quality solutions and services that will propel your company towards its end goal.\\u00a0<\\/p><p>As we strive to be the leading technology provider in the region and place our mark in the global map,\\u00a0<span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">bneXt<\\/span>\\u00a0commits to service excellence in all our undertaking by providing and sustaining valuable resources with deep technology and industry expertise.\\u00a0<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"9cb2da1\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Our methodology\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>bneXt classifies its methodology into two types of engagements:\\u00a0<\\/p><p><span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">Transformation Projects\\u00a0<\\/span>\\u2013 Larger green-field projects that are typically a fresh-install, rip-or-replace or a new innovation that will dramatically remodel an existing practice or solution. The steps involved will include:\\u00a0<\\/p><ol><li><span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">Design\\u00a0<\\/span>\\u2013 Deep-level analysis of business issues and crafting of a Transformation Design through Design Thinking workshops or similar activities \\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/li><li><span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">Build\\u00a0<\\/span>\\u2013 Phased execution depending on the Transformation Design agreed with the customer which include Project Management and Execution, Change Management and Stakeholder Engagement \\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/li><li><span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">Close-Out\\u00a0<\\/span>- Cut-over and Sign-off of a successful project \\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/li><\\/ol><p><span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">Transition Projects\\u00a0<\\/span>\\u2013 Projects that move from an existing business-as-usual model to a new design or managed-service model:\\u00a0<\\/p><ol><li><span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">Design\\u00a0<\\/span>\\u2013 Analysis of selected Business-as-Usual (BAU) or lights-on operations being considered for shifting to Managed Services using Process Mapping and Transition Design as well as review of Service Catalogs and definition of Service Level Agreements \\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/li><li><span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">Shift\\u00a0<\\/span>\\u2013 Phased execution depending on the Transition Design agreed with the customer which include Project Management and Execution, Change Management and Stakeholder Engagement; Resource, Knowledge and Assets Lift-and-Drop or Transform-and-Shift \\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/li><li><span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">Continuous Improvement\\u00a0<\\/span>- Regular executive reporting and improvements to processes and systems \\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/li><\\/ol>\",\"_id\":\"599b880\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Our resources\",\"tab_content\":\"<p><span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">bneXt<\\/span>\\u00a0prides itself in hiring only the best talents in the industry that will help you transform your\\u00a0<span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">Digital Core<\\/span>. We ensure that resources are also continuously updated in their knowledge skills via our\\u00a0<span class=\\\"x-el x-el-span px_-letter-spacing-normal px_-text-transform-none px_-fs-unset px_-ff-_Lato___arial__sans-serif px_-fw-700 x-d-ux\\\">Technology Academy<\\/span>. We also provide experimental labs to ensure that bleeding-edge technologies are first tested prior to deployment to our customers.\\u00a0<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"1ba8597\"}]},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"accordion\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
