(149,	1,	'2018-12-03 08:41:20',	'2018-12-03 08:41:20',	'[hbupro_banner id=\"151\"]\r\n<a>Your partner in digital transformation</a>\r\n\r\nIn todays exponential explosion of technologies, it is imperative for every company to disrupt itself before the industry disrupts and eliminates it. Along with the shift of technologies is the shift of business models and organizational cultures that add to the pressures of not only coping with but leading the pack. The variety of solutions, methodologies and services also add to the confusion of business leaders.\r\n\r\nAmidst how complicated the business world has become, bneXt helps you find what you want to BE NEXT as a company and help you plot your course and create a roadmap towards Digital Transformation where each of the segments defined are in sync with your objectives, priorities, structure and culture.\r\n\r\nBeyond the roadmap, bneXt helps you execute each defined segment by providing quality solutions and services that will propel your company towards its end goal.\r\n\r\nAs we strive to be the leading technology provider in the region and place our mark in the global map, bneXt commits to service excellence in all our undertaking by providing and sustaining valuable resources with deep technology and industry expertise.\r\n\r\n<a>Our methodology</a>\r\n\r\nbneXt classifies its methodology into two types of engagements:\r\n\r\nTransformation Projects  Larger green-field projects that are typically a fresh-install, rip-or-replace or a new innovation that will dramatically remodel an existing practice or solution. The steps involved will include:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Design  Deep-level analysis of business issues and crafting of a Transformation Design through Design Thinking workshops or similar activities</li>\r\n 	<li>Build  Phased execution depending on the Transformation Design agreed with the customer which include Project Management and Execution, Change Management and Stakeholder Engagement</li>\r\n 	<li>Close-Out  Cut-over and Sign-off of a successful project</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nTransition Projects  Projects that move from an existing business-as-usual model to a new design or managed-service model:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Design  Analysis of selected Business-as-Usual (BAU) or lights-on operations being considered for shifting to Managed Services using Process Mapping and Transition Design as well as review of Service Catalogs and definition of Service Level Agreements</li>\r\n 	<li>Shift  Phased execution depending on the Transition Design agreed with the customer which include Project Management and Execution, Change Management and Stakeholder Engagement; Resource, Knowledge and Assets Lift-and-Drop or Transform-and-Shift</li>\r\n 	<li>Continuous Improvement  Regular executive reporting and improvements to processes and systems</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<a>Our resources</a>\r\n\r\nbneXt prides itself in hiring only the best talents in the industry that will help you transform your Digital Core. We ensure that resources are also continuously updated in their knowledge skills via our Technology Academy. We also provide experimental labs to ensure that bleeding-edge technologies are first tested prior to deployment to our customers.',	'Who we are',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'who-we-are',	'',	'',	'2018-12-05 03:12:42',	'2018-12-05 03:12:42',	'',	0,	'http://104.238.96.209/~project/joroni/bnext2/?page_id=149',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
